The Captain, this Master of the World, and these two men?
Evidently they planned to take aboard the last of their wood.
Then they would withdraw within their machine, and go to sleep.
Would not that be the time to surprise them, before they could defend themselves?
Rather than to attempt to reach and capture the ship in face of this resolute Captain who was guarding it, Wells and I agreed that it was better to let his men return unassailed, and wait till they were all asleep.
It was now half an hour after ten.
